=== MIND_WEAVER ===
# id: 30
# title: The Mind Weaver
# chinese_title: 织心者
# category: Alien
# mode: dungeon

A chitinous alien crouches in the corner, its compound eyes tracking your movement. Silken threads connect it to the walls, forming a web that pulses with faint electrical signals. It projects an image into your mind: a question mark, followed by a handshake.

* [Accept the mental handshake]
  ~ gain_radical("手")
  "手" (shǒu) — hand, skill
* [Offer a memory as a gift]
  ~ gain_xp(25)
  "忆" (yì) — memory, to remember
* [Sever the mental connection]
  ~ gain_item("neural_boost")
  "断" (duàn) — to cut, to sever
